Net::BCCN
==============

Net::BCCN provides compact implementation of the BCCN notification protocol

    BCCN Broadcast Channel Notifications
    https://github.com/cade-vs/bccn

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

Net::BCCN does not use libraries other than core perl.

